text: Brewing stands have an extra item form corresponding to its block ID, which can be obtained via inventory editors with numeric item ID 117. It is not intended to be obtained in conventional gameplay.
Brewing stand items can now be obtained in singleplayer worlds via the /give command using the respective numeric ID.
The direct item form of brewing stands has been removed from the game. It can no longer exist as an item in any way, only as a placed block.
Brewing stands exist as an item.
The brewing stand item uses this texture in inventories, when held in first or third person view, as a dropped item or when in an item frame.
The brewing stand item now uses the aforementioned texture when in an item frame.
